Title: Day 5: 1:00 A.M. - 2:00 A.M.
Plot: Jack captures Henderson and attempts to force him to hand over the recording, but Henderson targets Heller to buy himself more time. Logan confesses his involvement in Palmer's assassination to a distraught Martha. Miles traces Chloe to Buchanan's home, but Hayes finds herself questioning Logan's motives as CTU closes in.
Writer: Craig Van Sickle, Steven Long Mitchell
GuestStars: Tracy Howe,  Jenny Levine,  William Devane,  Bernard K. Addison,  Adam Donshik,  Carl Gilliard,  Marc Raducci
